      .container-fluid
        .row
          .col-md-5.col-md-offset-1
            .copy-wrap
              h2.heading.no-margin-md
                span.title.title--large Let's <em>end</em> <br class="visible-lg-block">gender inequality.
                span.sub-heading
                  | We're calling attention to the wage gap <br class="visible-lg-block">with a sitewide sale. <span class="hidden-xs hidden-sm">Here's why it matters.</span>

              .cta-wrapper
                span.btn-md.btn-featured
